      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MISS ENVY (5) shapes well for this after winning last start over the 600m at The Meadows in a brilliant 34.24. In form and rates on top again. VALENZUELA (4) hit the ground running from the squeeze draw with a slick early split, holding on for a minor placing when third and beaten one length at The Meadows over 600m in 34.30. Has performed well from this box with a win and three minor placings to his name from five starts. Expecting another good run. INTIMIDATION (1) was on speed settling but found some traffic when checked, missing the frame to finish fifth (27.77) at Mandurah in a OPEN. Key player if finds best. SCARLETT'S BOY (2) was in the money last start despite a big quote and is likely to feature again.",
